cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object tracking using detectors and online learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a co-tracking approach that involves co-learning of two detectors. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses uncertainty sampling to improve the accuracy and speed of the system. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in videos. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a tracking system that can be used in robotics applications.
